承保公司，承保公司同意后以书面形式委托当地保险公司代查勘、代定损并拍损失照片。事故处理完毕带回代查勘报告，代定损清单、照片向承保公司索赔。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#337fe5;font-size:14px;\">3、保险车辆在外地出险如何报案？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 保险车辆在停放中被盗或在使用过程中被抢劫，经向公安部门报案，在三个月以上仍未破案，提供以下材料向承保公司索赔：向当地登报启事，市、区县公安刑侦部门的报案证明、购车发票、车辆所有权益转让书等有关证明材料。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>','article.state.normal','普通','visible.true','显示',0,'2011-09-28 08:09:01','rongzhan','融展集团'),(25,'rongzhan.service.book','在线预约','<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">预约请到融展集团旗下各4S店:</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">吉林省：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><a href=\"http://175.19.187.218:8080/rongzhan/infiniti/cus_bookcar.jsp?cid=infiniti.book\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">长春融展英菲</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">尼迪专营店</span></a></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\"></span></span><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://175.19.187.218:8080/rongzhan/ruihe/cus_bookcar.jsp?cid=ruihe.book\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">东风日产吉林</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">融展瑞合专营店</span></a></span> </span></span><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://175.19.187.218:8080/rongzhan/xinyu/cus_bookcar.jsp?